     The mother of all soups.

   ?: A simple high-level script 
   used to generate Ubuntu based
   live distros using the Debian
   Live framework.

   Broth is at the moment focussed 
   on producing Puredyne live 
   images but it can be used for 
   virtually any other live systems.

   Doc: ./broth -h

